WEBVTT

01:37.840 --> 01:41.020
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.130 --> 01:43.960
[Episode 21]

01:51.310 --> 01:52.910
Mr. Ji, you didn't call me out

01:53.310 --> 01:54.310
just to accompany you

01:54.310 --> 01:55.840
to pick up a teacup, did you?

01:57.280 --> 01:58.479
You gave me the tea.

01:58.479 --> 01:59.759
So it's only right to ask your opinion

01:59.759 --> 02:00.920
on what kind of teacup

02:00.920 --> 02:01.980
would be suitable.

02:03.850 --> 02:04.630
By the way,

02:05.280 --> 02:06.350
how's your hand

02:06.350 --> 02:07.920
doing after earlier today?

02:09.280 --> 02:09.880
It's fine.

02:16.590 --> 02:17.190
It's fine.

02:19.390 --> 02:20.560
It's getting late.

02:21.840 --> 02:22.850
Just walk me this far.

02:22.850 --> 02:24.079
It's not much further ahead.

02:24.079 --> 02:25.240
-I can walk back by myself.
-It's okay.

02:25.240 --> 02:26.440
It's just a few steps.

02:26.710 --> 02:28.110
You really don't have to.

02:37.070 --> 02:38.630
What happened that night...

02:38.630 --> 02:39.690
It was an accident.

02:40.910 --> 02:41.710
Wasn't it?

02:44.030 --> 02:44.750
Yes,

02:45.560 --> 02:46.680
it was an accident.

02:48.470 --> 02:49.680
And on top of that,

02:50.310 --> 02:51.560
I was running a fever.

02:51.579 --> 02:52.630
Could barely stand.

02:52.630 --> 02:53.910
So...

02:53.910 --> 02:55.310
I accidentally...

02:57.079 --> 02:58.740
I just want to say sorry to you.

02:58.750 --> 02:59.750
I caused you

03:00.280 --> 03:01.030
too much trouble that night.

03:01.030 --> 03:01.910
It's fine.

03:03.790 --> 03:05.050
Let's forget about it.

03:10.470 --> 03:11.310
Okay.

03:12.750 --> 03:13.680
Let's forget it.

03:19.290 --> 03:20.470
It's getting late.

03:20.470 --> 03:21.680
I'll go back now.

03:22.030 --> 03:23.030
Get some rest.

03:23.210 --> 03:24.010
Okay.

03:24.400 --> 03:25.190
Good night.

03:25.750 --> 03:26.470
Good night.

03:37.329 --> 03:39.140
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

03:40.840 --> 03:42.480
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

03:41.310 --> 03:42.210
Miyu.

03:42.470 --> 03:43.670
Now, do you still want

03:43.680 --> 03:45.910
to start a new relationship?

03:44.700 --> 03:46.610
♪ People in the city ♪

03:47.430 --> 03:50.370
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

03:49.840 --> 03:51.079
Maybe it's because we've been through

03:51.079 --> 03:52.890
so much together at work.

03:52.300 --> 03:54.110
♪ The palms of time ♪

03:53.120 --> 03:54.560
Or maybe it's because he's helped me out

03:54.560 --> 03:56.230
so many times.

03:56.010 --> 03:59.150
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

03:56.700 --> 03:57.500
I admit.

03:58.120 --> 03:59.570
I have fallen

03:59.730 --> 04:00.450
for this man.

03:59.760 --> 04:02.680
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

04:01.840 --> 04:02.520
In the past,

04:02.520 --> 04:03.560
I wouldn't have hesitated

04:03.560 --> 04:05.000
to see where it went.

04:03.680 --> 04:05.720
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

04:05.850 --> 04:06.890
But now?

04:07.200 --> 04:10.400
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

04:07.590 --> 04:08.680
I've just got out of

04:08.680 --> 04:09.860
a failed marriage

04:10.520 --> 04:11.650
and been back at work.

04:10.990 --> 04:14.020
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

04:11.960 --> 04:13.630
I still have a huge debt to pay.

04:13.950 --> 04:14.860
Love

04:14.610 --> 04:17.730
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

04:15.310 --> 04:17.310
isn't going to be the cure to my life.

04:17.870 --> 04:21.160
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

04:18.470 --> 04:20.950
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

04:22.510 --> 04:25.820
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

04:26.370 --> 04:29.740
♪ The forgotten past ♪

04:30.720 --> 04:32.990
♪ There may be regrets ♪

04:34.650 --> 04:36.890
♪ There may be loneliness ♪

05:20.530 --> 05:23.540
[Charoro]

05:31.000 --> 05:32.060
It doesn't matter.

05:33.750 --> 05:35.010
Let's forget about it.

05:41.510 --> 05:43.110
[Charoro]

05:43.330 --> 05:44.470
[Charoro]

05:49.930 --> 05:52.240
[Haven't been in touch for a while.
I guess you haven't changed your number.]

05:54.150 --> 05:56.180
[Haven't been in touch for a while.
I guess you haven't changed your number.]

05:54.270 --> 05:56.000
Haven't been in touch for a while.

05:56.000 --> 05:57.690
I guess you haven't changed your number.

05:56.210 --> 05:58.030
[I'm glad you're back.
Let's meet up sometime.]

05:58.060 --> 05:58.550
[Jiang Zhichun]

05:58.530 --> 06:00.140
I'm glad you're back.

06:00.480 --> 06:02.160
Let's meet up sometime.

06:04.580 --> 06:07.920
[BBQ]

06:05.160 --> 06:05.830
Ma'am.

06:05.830 --> 06:06.830
Is everyone here?

06:07.160 --> 06:07.800
They're waiting for you.

06:07.800 --> 06:08.600
In the back.

06:09.040 --> 06:09.800
I'll take you there.

06:09.800 --> 06:10.800
This way, please.

06:11.560 --> 06:12.430
There are others?

06:12.430 --> 06:13.480
All the way in the back.

06:13.480 --> 06:14.610
Got it. You go ahead.

06:14.610 --> 06:17.150
[Spicy]

06:15.160 --> 06:15.920
Who's it?

06:27.310 --> 06:27.940
Mr. Guo,

06:28.350 --> 06:29.540
I've invited her here.

06:29.540 --> 06:31.100
You should do the talking.

06:33.310 --> 06:34.250
Chef Li,

06:35.000 --> 06:37.040
all those problems
in the Chinese restaurant—

06:37.040 --> 06:38.770
I didn't cause them on purpose.

06:39.040 --> 06:39.560
But

06:39.560 --> 06:40.690
I didn't do anything to stop it.

06:40.690 --> 06:42.040
I failed in my duty.

06:42.040 --> 06:44.040
I, Guo Luda, cannot shirk the blame.

06:45.240 --> 06:45.720
Of course,

06:45.720 --> 06:46.830
bringing this up now

06:46.830 --> 06:48.890
seems a bit like beating a dead horse.

06:49.040 --> 06:51.240
But these are truly my honest thoughts.

06:51.560 --> 06:52.720
When the Chinese restaurant opened,

06:52.720 --> 06:54.360
I really didn't swap the cured pork.

06:54.360 --> 06:55.480
I'm not well-educated,

06:55.480 --> 06:56.720
but I know right from wrong.

06:56.720 --> 06:58.430
If I had done something like that,

06:58.430 --> 07:01.290
my late master wouldn't
forgive me, even in heaven.

07:04.600 --> 07:05.560
Chef,

07:05.560 --> 07:07.240
my brothers and I here

07:07.240 --> 07:08.720
are neither Chef Jia's men

07:08.720 --> 07:10.120
nor Wei's men.

07:10.480 --> 07:11.120
We all

07:11.120 --> 07:13.560
studied under Zheng Shuolin,
the great Huaiyang cuisine master.

07:13.560 --> 07:14.800
We started from

07:14.800 --> 07:16.360
small family restaurants,

07:16.560 --> 07:18.560
got bought out by Purong Hotel,

07:18.560 --> 07:20.160
and stayed on in the kitchen.

07:20.240 --> 07:22.500
We earned our place here with real skill.

07:22.720 --> 07:24.920
I hope you can see that.

07:26.720 --> 07:27.780
Let's go in and sit.

07:27.920 --> 07:29.560
There are still many things you don't know

07:29.560 --> 07:31.020
that they want to tell you.

07:33.720 --> 07:35.360
Then take a seat, chefs.

07:37.360 --> 07:38.159
Ma'am.

07:39.159 --> 07:41.090
We'll take 200 lamb skewers first.

07:41.159 --> 07:42.920
Okay, coming right up.

07:43.480 --> 07:44.040
Cheers.

07:44.800 --> 07:45.360
Cheers.

07:49.450 --> 07:52.780
[Purong By Your Side]

07:50.390 --> 07:51.159
Come in.

07:54.390 --> 07:55.240
Ms. Yang,

07:56.040 --> 07:57.000
you're looking for me?

07:57.000 --> 07:57.830
Ms. Xu,

07:58.240 --> 07:59.040
you applied

07:59.040 --> 08:01.560
for the career direction
assessment test, right?

08:01.560 --> 08:02.270
Yes.

08:02.270 --> 08:03.560
But I'm not qualified

08:03.560 --> 08:05.240
to take this test yet, right?

08:05.360 --> 08:06.600
The general manager's office

08:06.600 --> 08:07.830
has reformed the employee

08:07.830 --> 08:09.000
development system.

08:09.000 --> 08:10.560
Employees who‘ve been here
for less than a year

08:10.560 --> 08:11.390
are now also entitled to know

08:11.390 --> 08:12.720
their career potential.

08:12.720 --> 08:13.360
I called you here

08:13.360 --> 08:14.390
just to let you know

08:14.390 --> 08:16.760
that you can take the test anytime.

08:17.560 --> 08:18.960
That's great. Thank you.

08:21.690 --> 08:23.870
[Purong Hotel
Career Direction Assessment Test]

08:21.830 --> 08:23.360
The test will take about

08:23.360 --> 08:25.000
45 to 60 minutes.

08:23.870 --> 08:24.830
[Work order]

08:24.850 --> 08:26.650
[Expenses] [Expenses Items]
[Your Authority (yuan): ]

08:25.000 --> 08:26.390
Just try to stay relaxed

08:26.390 --> 08:27.830
while you're completing it.

08:26.680 --> 08:27.600
[Work time]

08:27.830 --> 08:28.600
Thank you.

08:39.340 --> 08:41.980
[Name: Xu Miyu]

08:52.670 --> 08:55.440
Purong represents a classic style of life

08:55.070 --> 09:02.940
[Purong Hotel]

08:55.510 --> 08:57.310
and a kind of top-level dignity.

08:57.480 --> 08:58.360
But

08:58.360 --> 08:59.390
at its core, a hotel

08:59.390 --> 09:00.960
exists to serve its guests

09:01.030 --> 09:03.030
and the people who live in this city.

09:03.030 --> 09:03.940
So,

09:04.200 --> 09:05.390
what's important

09:05.390 --> 09:07.520
is stay connected with current trends

09:07.550 --> 09:09.670
and promote the Purong lifestyle

09:09.670 --> 09:11.390
to more guests.

09:17.590 --> 09:18.280
True.

09:19.000 --> 09:21.000
Adding items that interest customers

09:21.000 --> 09:22.840
does help boost revenue.

09:23.200 --> 09:23.960
So,

09:24.270 --> 09:25.600
colleagues from sales—

09:25.620 --> 09:26.980
[Customer Repurchase Intention Survey]

09:25.930 --> 09:28.060
We're planning to launch a new package

09:28.080 --> 09:29.170
for the 520 promotion.

09:29.170 --> 09:30.290
Ms. Xu,

09:30.320 --> 09:31.890
there's noise in Room 1810.

09:31.740 --> 09:32.820
[Customer Repurchase Intention Survey]

09:31.910 --> 09:34.370
The guest next door
has already complained.

09:35.670 --> 09:36.800
I'll be right there.

10:01.730 --> 10:03.120
Look.

10:10.240 --> 10:11.000
Miyu.

10:11.680 --> 10:13.330
These are my old friends.

10:13.600 --> 10:14.840
None of us have anything to do now.

10:14.840 --> 10:15.630
so we're just

10:15.630 --> 10:16.510
having fun.

10:17.840 --> 10:18.860
Daniel,

10:18.940 --> 10:20.480
I understand what you want to do,

10:20.480 --> 10:21.630
but

10:21.630 --> 10:24.060
the hotel is a semi-public
place after all.

10:24.120 --> 10:26.480
Other guests are already complaining.

10:26.480 --> 10:27.840
So if you want to rehearse together,

10:27.840 --> 10:30.440
you probably can't do it
on the executive floor

10:31.150 --> 10:32.750
It is a bit disturbing.

10:33.750 --> 10:35.630
But where can we go?

10:38.150 --> 10:39.480
Let me figure this out.

10:51.910 --> 10:53.310
Watch out for the uphill.

11:00.120 --> 11:01.120
Here we are.

11:08.550 --> 11:09.070
Come.

11:09.390 --> 11:10.290
Come on.

11:14.280 --> 11:15.160
Be careful.

11:18.320 --> 11:18.910
Look.

11:19.720 --> 11:20.850
This place

11:20.880 --> 11:22.000
doesn't have many people around.

11:22.000 --> 11:23.360
There are warehouses on both sides,

11:23.360 --> 11:24.600
so it won't disturb anyone's work.

11:24.600 --> 11:26.240
It's perfect for your rehearsals.

11:26.240 --> 11:27.000
Also,

11:27.000 --> 11:29.200
I've prepared power strips and chairs.

11:30.130 --> 11:31.940
There is a clothes rack here

11:32.110 --> 11:34.060
for you to hang your clothes.

11:35.180 --> 11:36.300
Miyu.

11:36.370 --> 11:37.380
Fantastic.

11:38.000 --> 11:39.000
How's it, old friends?

11:39.000 --> 11:39.600
Great.

11:41.130 --> 11:42.130
Good.

11:43.750 --> 11:44.880
This is outrageous.

11:45.210 --> 11:47.450
You secretly moved
a band with an average age of over 70

11:47.260 --> 11:49.590
[Purong Hotel]

11:47.480 --> 11:48.840
to the basement warehouse.

11:48.840 --> 11:50.000
What were you thinking?

11:50.000 --> 11:51.480
I know that place has no windows

11:51.480 --> 11:52.550
and poor ventilation.

11:52.550 --> 11:54.000
So I agreed with them

11:54.000 --> 11:56.000
that daily rehearsals
can't exceed one hour.

11:56.000 --> 11:58.000
If any accidents happen within that hour,

11:58.000 --> 11:59.530
how do you plan to handle it?

12:00.720 --> 12:01.580
I'm sorry.

12:02.000 --> 12:03.600
I’ll go find another place.

12:05.640 --> 12:07.300
Why didn't you ask me for help?

12:16.530 --> 12:17.630
Forget it.

12:18.120 --> 12:19.720
Bring the seniors out first.

12:19.840 --> 12:20.630
From now on,

12:20.630 --> 12:21.720
don't let guests

12:22.120 --> 12:24.520
use that storage room without my approval.

12:35.810 --> 12:36.810
Help me check

12:36.840 --> 12:37.480
all the currently available

12:37.480 --> 12:38.910
empty spaces in the hotel.

12:38.910 --> 12:39.860
Soundproof

12:40.000 --> 12:41.240
and well-ventilated.

12:41.240 --> 12:43.320
Ms. Xu just left with a long face.

12:43.320 --> 12:44.000
Thank you.

12:44.000 --> 12:45.480
Did you pick on her again?

12:44.790 --> 12:48.670
[Purong Hotel]

12:45.720 --> 12:47.000
Who picked on her?

12:49.240 --> 12:49.840
Wait.

12:50.840 --> 12:53.300
Is there something
going on between you two?

12:53.400 --> 12:54.790
Just get to the point.

12:56.510 --> 12:57.840
Mr. Zheng from the Lusia University

12:57.840 --> 12:58.960
Alumni Association

12:58.960 --> 13:00.450
will be here soon.

13:01.120 --> 13:02.240
He wants to go over

13:02.240 --> 13:05.170
the activity flow
for the 60th anniversary reunion.

13:05.360 --> 13:06.960
Isn't it basically settled?

13:07.120 --> 13:09.430
They want to add a small request.

13:09.510 --> 13:10.240
They said they'd like

13:10.240 --> 13:12.240
to look for the old Shanghai vibe.

13:12.360 --> 13:14.240
Should we put on a cheongsam show

13:14.240 --> 13:16.720
or a medley of classic old songs?

13:17.000 --> 13:18.360
If we really turn the banquet hall

13:18.360 --> 13:20.000
into old Shanghai style,

13:20.000 --> 13:20.840
then we will

13:21.240 --> 13:22.840
have to spend more money.

13:24.240 --> 13:25.480
And we might

13:25.480 --> 13:26.480
mess it up.

13:28.120 --> 13:28.960
It's too hard.

13:33.710 --> 13:34.360
Old man.

13:34.360 --> 13:36.020
Take one more step. I dare you.

13:36.270 --> 13:37.980
I've told you many times.

13:38.080 --> 13:38.720
Daniel,

13:39.120 --> 13:40.240
my colleagues
from the Engineering Department

13:40.240 --> 13:41.600
are just doing their job.

13:41.600 --> 13:42.440
The main issue

13:42.440 --> 13:43.720
is this place is too risky.

13:43.720 --> 13:45.480
The hotel cannot bear this responsibility.

13:45.480 --> 13:46.740
What responsibility?

13:46.750 --> 13:48.480
To put it bluntly,
you're afraid we'll die here,

13:48.480 --> 13:49.120
right?

13:49.600 --> 13:52.320
Drawing a conclusion
without considering probability—

13:52.320 --> 13:53.480
that's a bit rogue.

13:53.840 --> 13:55.290
Daniel, calm down.

13:55.340 --> 13:57.000
The hotel has its concerns,

13:57.000 --> 13:58.510
but it's mainly to ensure

13:58.510 --> 14:00.720
the health and safety of the guests.

14:00.720 --> 14:02.650
Ji Feng told you to say this, right?

14:04.120 --> 14:06.600
Go ask him. I helped him

14:06.600 --> 14:08.110
fix the Chinese restaurant's design,

14:08.110 --> 14:09.770
and now he turns his back on me?

14:10.360 --> 14:11.440
If he's got the guts,

14:11.440 --> 14:13.240
let him come kick us out himself.

14:13.320 --> 14:14.780
It's a misunderstanding.

14:15.480 --> 14:17.000
Definitely a misunderstanding.

14:17.000 --> 14:17.720
Look,

14:18.510 --> 14:20.110
it's too stuffy here,

14:20.140 --> 14:21.670
and the air quality is poor.

14:21.720 --> 14:23.710
Ms. Xu and I discussed it.

14:24.080 --> 14:25.120
Right next

14:25.120 --> 14:25.980
to

14:26.010 --> 14:26.870
the restaurant on the second floor,

14:26.870 --> 14:28.440
we've set aside a space

14:28.480 --> 14:29.880
just for you to rehearse.

14:30.320 --> 14:31.360
If you're willing

14:31.360 --> 14:32.840
to move upstairs,

14:33.000 --> 14:33.480
no one

14:33.480 --> 14:35.010
will ever bother you again.

14:35.200 --> 14:36.630
You can focus on

14:36.630 --> 14:37.470
practicing.

14:38.480 --> 14:39.240
Really?

14:42.640 --> 14:44.010
How about we go and have a look first?

14:44.010 --> 14:45.240
-See if you like it.
-Yes.

14:45.240 --> 14:46.120
That's fine.

14:46.840 --> 14:47.840
We can take a look.

14:47.870 --> 14:48.800
I'll take you up.

14:48.830 --> 14:49.350
Come on.

14:51.120 --> 14:51.840
Come.

14:54.720 --> 14:55.360
Please.

14:59.840 --> 15:00.600
Not bad.

15:01.240 --> 15:02.240
What do you think?

15:04.320 --> 15:05.480
Not bad.

15:09.480 --> 15:10.360
Not bad.

15:11.120 --> 15:13.200
The environment here isn't the best yet,

15:13.200 --> 15:14.320
But don't worry,

15:14.480 --> 15:15.880
we'll keep improving it.

15:16.230 --> 15:17.510
But...

15:17.510 --> 15:19.120
nothing comes for free.

15:20.120 --> 15:21.440
Are you

15:21.840 --> 15:23.440
asking me for another favor?

15:25.000 --> 15:25.630
As expected,

15:25.630 --> 15:27.830
I can't hide anything from you, Mr. Tan.

15:28.000 --> 15:29.440
I do have something

15:29.440 --> 15:30.480
that I hope you can help with.

15:30.480 --> 15:31.120
Tell me.

15:33.870 --> 15:35.960
The alumni reunion of Lusia University

15:35.960 --> 15:37.690
is going to be held at our hotel.

15:37.720 --> 15:38.720
The attendees are all

15:38.720 --> 15:40.360
elderly people.

15:40.360 --> 15:41.480
And what they want to hear the most

15:41.480 --> 15:42.200
are the claasic

15:42.200 --> 15:43.790
old Shanghai jazz tunes

15:43.960 --> 15:46.120
from their younger days.

15:46.870 --> 15:48.000
That's exactly

15:48.000 --> 15:49.860
the kind of music you love to play.

15:50.120 --> 15:51.120
And you guys are here

15:51.120 --> 15:52.720
at our hotel at the same time.

15:52.960 --> 15:53.750
So,

15:54.060 --> 15:55.300
maybe it's fate.

15:58.840 --> 15:59.580
That's good.

16:04.750 --> 16:05.840
Great.

16:06.120 --> 16:07.400
It's fate.

16:15.000 --> 16:15.600
Ms. Xu.

16:17.840 --> 16:19.340
I didn't discuss this

16:19.450 --> 16:20.800
with you beforehand.

16:21.840 --> 16:23.120
Mr. Ji, you don't need

16:23.120 --> 16:25.180
my opinion for any decision you make.

16:25.240 --> 16:26.480
Besides, this is my job.

16:26.480 --> 16:27.600
I didn't do it well.

16:27.600 --> 16:29.080
I'll go back and reflect on it.

16:29.080 --> 16:30.080
Don't say that.

16:30.080 --> 16:32.430
Meeting the guests' needs
is your responsibility.

16:32.430 --> 16:34.200
Supporting you is mine.

16:37.360 --> 16:38.950
I mean—

16:38.980 --> 16:41.110
a superior supporting a subordinate.

16:44.840 --> 16:46.840
I have something else to do. I'll...

16:47.360 --> 16:48.690
No matter what happens,

16:48.750 --> 16:50.150
I hope you won't avoid me.

16:50.720 --> 16:52.420
I'm your superior.

16:52.790 --> 16:54.360
I will take responsibility for you.

16:54.360 --> 16:56.020
You can trust me a little more,

16:56.200 --> 16:56.750
okay?

17:00.480 --> 17:02.140
I've said what I needed to say.

17:05.440 --> 17:06.240
Coming?

17:16.720 --> 17:17.589
According

17:17.589 --> 17:18.720
to the data from our

17:18.720 --> 17:20.240
Business Management Department,

17:20.240 --> 17:22.109
the Chinese restaurant's revenue
has hit a new high

17:22.109 --> 17:23.970
in the first week since it  opened.

17:24.589 --> 17:27.790
The occupancy rate of
HSKP Department is also steadily climbing—

17:27.790 --> 17:29.390
far beyond our projections.

17:33.030 --> 17:34.720
That's enough of the good news.

17:34.720 --> 17:36.000
Next, let's have

17:36.000 --> 17:37.110
Mr. Xue

17:37.110 --> 17:37.830
brief us

17:37.830 --> 17:39.560
on tomorrow's reception work.

17:48.550 --> 17:50.400
The number of the alumni group tomorrow

17:50.400 --> 17:51.310
is over 100.

17:51.720 --> 17:52.380
Among them,

17:52.830 --> 17:54.720
there are 68 seniors

17:54.720 --> 17:56.120
who are over 80 years old.

17:56.640 --> 17:58.110
We need to accommodate their needs

17:58.110 --> 17:59.430
as much as possible.

17:59.510 --> 18:00.240
For example,

18:00.240 --> 18:01.880
the lighting and ventilation

18:01.880 --> 18:02.940
in the guest rooms,

18:03.110 --> 18:05.240
and the guests' dietary preferences.

18:05.440 --> 18:06.440
If necessary,

18:06.440 --> 18:08.570
we can provide some medical services.

18:12.310 --> 18:12.960
Hello.

18:13.000 --> 18:14.130
I'd like to check in.

18:16.400 --> 18:18.600
You'd like a south-facing room, right?

18:18.640 --> 18:19.110
Yes.

18:19.240 --> 18:20.370
Let me check for you.

18:20.840 --> 18:23.690
[Room Status Center]

18:25.340 --> 18:29.110
[Executive Room 1812]

18:28.790 --> 18:29.640
He...

18:30.190 --> 18:31.400
checked out?

18:43.220 --> 18:44.960
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

18:46.730 --> 18:48.370
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

18:50.590 --> 18:52.500
♪ People in the city ♪

18:53.320 --> 18:56.260
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

18:58.190 --> 19:00.000
♪ The palms of time ♪

19:01.900 --> 19:05.040
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

19:05.650 --> 19:08.570
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

19:09.570 --> 19:11.610
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

19:13.090 --> 19:16.290
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

19:16.880 --> 19:19.910
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

19:20.500 --> 19:23.620
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

19:24.360 --> 19:26.840
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

19:27.010 --> 19:28.210
Room service.

19:28.400 --> 19:31.710
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

19:32.260 --> 19:35.630
♪ The forgotten past ♪

19:36.440 --> 19:37.820
Good morning, Mr. Ji.

19:36.610 --> 19:38.880
♪ There may be regrets ♪

19:39.590 --> 19:40.030
Hello, Mr. Ji.

19:40.030 --> 19:41.380
I am the 10th-floor forewoman.

19:40.540 --> 19:42.780
♪ There may be loneliness ♪

19:41.400 --> 19:43.660
Feel free to call me if you need anything.

19:43.770 --> 19:44.640
Thank you.

20:12.400 --> 20:16.530
[Lusia University Alumni Association
Anniversary Reunion]

20:16.670 --> 20:17.640
[Alumni Association of Lusia University]

20:17.660 --> 20:19.470
[60th Anniversary of Establishment]

20:21.400 --> 20:22.310
The car to the airport

20:22.310 --> 20:23.550
has already left.

20:24.880 --> 20:26.080
Why go to the airport?

20:30.590 --> 20:31.660
Sorry.

20:31.680 --> 20:32.400
My mistake.

20:32.430 --> 20:33.160
Go on.

20:34.710 --> 20:36.110
Two shuttles each
in the morning and afternoon.

20:36.110 --> 20:37.390
That should guarantee

20:37.440 --> 20:38.480
none of the guests

20:38.480 --> 20:39.720
from the Lusia Alumni Association

20:39.720 --> 20:42.310
wait more than
half an hour at the airport.

20:47.680 --> 20:48.480
What's wrong?

20:48.640 --> 20:51.040
Moving rooms got you feeling sentimental?

20:52.780 --> 20:53.580
Not at all.

20:57.000 --> 20:58.460
Just make do for a few days.

20:58.720 --> 21:00.720
Once the alumni association leaves,

21:00.720 --> 21:02.890
I'll give 1812 back to you right away.

21:03.660 --> 21:05.190
I'm fine staying anywhere.

21:06.840 --> 21:07.400
By the way,

21:07.400 --> 21:09.330
has the car to the airport left yet?

21:11.790 --> 21:12.680
Mr. Ji,

21:13.240 --> 21:15.040
what was I just reporting to you?

21:17.510 --> 21:20.000
I... I asked the wrong question.
I meant to ask about

21:20.000 --> 21:20.480
the banquet hall.

21:20.480 --> 21:22.400
16 tables, 182 people.

21:25.480 --> 21:26.480
By the way, Mr. Ji.

21:27.240 --> 21:29.700
How many alumni are coming
to reunion again?

21:41.000 --> 21:41.750
Mr. Ji,

21:42.790 --> 21:44.720
who exactly is on your mind?

21:45.680 --> 21:46.720
No one.

21:46.720 --> 21:48.240
I stayed up late last night

21:48.240 --> 21:49.550
and didn't sleep well.

21:49.550 --> 21:50.750
My brain is a bit slow.

21:51.270 --> 21:52.870
You're just being stubborn.

21:53.160 --> 21:54.270
As your senior,

21:54.720 --> 21:56.920
let me give you a little piece of advice.

21:57.480 --> 21:59.240
When your heart starts churning,

21:59.240 --> 22:01.680
just think of Duan Aoxiang
staring you down.

22:01.680 --> 22:02.720
And think about

22:02.720 --> 22:05.180
the cutthroat competition in the industry.

22:06.240 --> 22:07.300
Works pretty well.

22:08.240 --> 22:09.440
What are you talking about?

22:09.440 --> 22:10.570
I don't understand.

22:10.920 --> 22:12.180
I'm going out for a bit.

22:16.750 --> 22:17.480
Mr. Ji.

22:18.000 --> 22:18.720
What is it?

22:19.720 --> 22:20.430
Mr. Ji,

22:20.640 --> 22:22.240
I'm here to deliver
the candidate materials

22:22.240 --> 22:24.240
for the front office lobby manager.

22:24.960 --> 22:26.510
Isn't Anna about to take maternity leave?

22:26.510 --> 22:27.440
Director Bai said

22:27.440 --> 22:30.040
we need to fill
the lobby manager role quickly.

22:30.210 --> 22:33.720
[Employee Internal Promotion
Application Form]

22:34.020 --> 22:40.410
[Lusia University Alumni Association
Anniversary Reunion]

22:36.270 --> 22:37.200
Put it here.

22:39.240 --> 22:40.700
A little further forward.

22:52.930 --> 22:53.480
Let me help you.

22:53.480 --> 22:54.680
Thanks, but I'm fine.

22:55.160 --> 22:56.720
Help me with the luggage.

22:56.720 --> 22:58.050
Okay. This way, please.

23:03.820 --> 23:04.500
[Alumni Association of Lusia University]

23:03.960 --> 23:04.880
Jialing!

23:04.520 --> 23:05.620
[60th Anniversary of Establishment]

23:05.790 --> 23:07.080
You're back too!

23:09.440 --> 23:10.720
My old deskmate!

23:10.720 --> 23:12.440
I've missed you so much!

23:12.550 --> 23:13.720
Meilan,

23:13.720 --> 23:15.440
it's been so many years.

23:15.440 --> 23:17.340
I'm so happy today.

23:18.070 --> 23:19.440
I'll take you to see Wang.

23:19.440 --> 23:21.240
He's been waiting for us all morning.

23:21.240 --> 23:22.310
Okay.

23:23.160 --> 23:25.480
It's been so many years.

23:29.440 --> 23:29.790
Hello.

23:29.790 --> 23:31.160
Your room is on the third floor.

23:31.160 --> 23:32.030
The elevator is over there.

23:32.030 --> 23:33.680
Just walk in that direction.

23:33.920 --> 23:34.640
Welcome.

23:40.640 --> 23:42.480
Why is there
such a long line at the reception?

23:42.480 --> 23:43.680
Clear it out quickly.

23:43.880 --> 23:45.000
Open another line here.

23:45.000 --> 23:45.720
Copy that.

23:46.640 --> 23:48.000
The reception is short of staff.

23:48.000 --> 23:48.730
We need help.

23:49.240 --> 23:50.000
Xu,

23:50.000 --> 23:51.070
the reception is short of staff.

23:51.070 --> 23:52.840
Come help with the check-in.

23:53.000 --> 23:53.480
Okay.

23:56.720 --> 23:57.510
Ms. An,

23:57.510 --> 23:58.400
are you okay?

24:03.270 --> 24:04.270
You go

24:04.750 --> 24:06.790
and turn on the check-in system first.

24:06.790 --> 24:07.650
I need a moment.

24:07.720 --> 24:08.510
Okay.

24:28.030 --> 24:29.100
Ms. Xu.

24:30.030 --> 24:30.860
Do you have

24:30.960 --> 24:33.290
a printed list of executive floor guests?

24:33.480 --> 24:34.720
All the guest lists are here.

24:34.720 --> 24:35.920
Look for yourselves.

24:36.720 --> 24:38.270
We'll go blind reading this.

24:38.270 --> 24:39.240
Ms. Xu,

24:39.240 --> 24:41.270
-I'll go back to the executive floor.
-Wait.

24:41.270 --> 24:42.730
I have a digital copy here.

24:42.890 --> 24:44.350
We'll print it ourselves.

24:44.790 --> 24:45.640
Give it to me.

24:48.720 --> 24:49.510
Ms. An.

24:50.480 --> 24:51.680
Ms. Xu,

24:51.680 --> 24:53.140
that's thoughtful of you.

24:53.270 --> 24:54.640
You don't look well.

24:54.640 --> 24:55.720
Go rest for a while.

24:56.720 --> 24:57.480
I'm fine.

24:58.030 --> 24:59.400
Thanks for your help.

24:59.480 --> 25:00.270
Be careful.

25:07.720 --> 25:08.310
Let me do it.

25:08.310 --> 25:08.720
Okay.

25:12.030 --> 25:12.750
Everyone,

25:13.070 --> 25:14.720
you can check in here too.

25:19.510 --> 25:20.400
Welcome.

25:21.400 --> 25:22.930
Help me find the materials.

25:25.270 --> 25:26.400
Please show your ID.

25:32.070 --> 25:33.310
No, this is too slow.

25:35.720 --> 25:37.720
Huanhuan, lend me your microphone.

25:37.720 --> 25:38.980
Xiaoyan, microphone.

25:43.070 --> 25:45.030
Dear guests
of the Lusia Alumni Association,

25:45.030 --> 25:46.070
hello, everyone,

25:46.160 --> 25:48.320
welcome to Purong Hotel.

25:48.400 --> 25:50.400
Next, the guests whose names I call,

25:50.400 --> 25:52.000
please bring your passports

25:52.000 --> 25:52.920
and come to me.

25:52.920 --> 25:54.550
I will take everyone upstairs

25:54.550 --> 25:56.240
to check in, okay?

25:57.480 --> 25:59.460
First, Ms. Fu Meilan.

25:59.640 --> 26:00.640
I'm here.

26:01.240 --> 26:01.590
This way.

26:01.590 --> 26:02.590
This way, please.

26:03.240 --> 26:04.640
Mr. Jing Zekai.

26:05.270 --> 26:06.000
Here.

26:06.240 --> 26:07.400
Ms. Qin Jialing.

26:07.720 --> 26:08.510
Here.

26:11.510 --> 26:13.270
M-My passport is in this suitcase.

26:13.270 --> 26:14.240
In the suitcase.

26:16.000 --> 26:16.550
It's fine.

26:16.550 --> 26:18.030
Who put this on top of it?

26:18.030 --> 26:19.200
Wait a moment.

26:19.480 --> 26:20.030
It's okay.

26:20.030 --> 26:20.720
Okay.

26:21.480 --> 26:22.270
Oh, really.

26:23.880 --> 26:24.750
I've got it.

26:29.290 --> 26:30.420
[Qin 1802]

26:30.640 --> 26:32.000
Please go upstairs and check in first.

26:32.000 --> 26:33.160
The bellman will bring your luggage

26:33.160 --> 26:34.240
to your room later.

26:34.240 --> 26:35.240
Thank you.

26:35.240 --> 26:36.170
You're welcome.

26:36.790 --> 26:37.660
Please follow me this way.

26:37.660 --> 26:38.510
Okay.

26:38.510 --> 26:39.480
Next,

26:40.000 --> 26:41.820
Mr. Xiao Qiankun.

26:42.070 --> 26:43.670
Hello, welcome to our hotel.

26:49.880 --> 26:50.480
Ms. An,

26:50.480 --> 26:51.280
what's wrong?

26:53.240 --> 26:54.480
Ms. An! Ms. An!

26:55.640 --> 26:56.720
Ms. An!

26:57.000 --> 26:58.000
-Ms. An!
-What’s wrong?

26:58.000 --> 26:59.100
Ms. An!

26:59.130 --> 27:00.270
Ms. An!

27:00.510 --> 27:01.480
Ms. An!

27:01.570 --> 27:02.480
Lay her flat.

27:03.000 --> 27:04.070
What should we do?

27:04.070 --> 27:06.600
Well, Director Bai isn't here either.

27:06.720 --> 27:07.780
Call an ambulance!

27:07.790 --> 27:09.310
Right, call an ambulance.

27:11.070 --> 27:11.880
Ms. An.

27:13.070 --> 27:13.880
It'll be fine.

27:14.000 --> 27:15.270
The ambulance will be here soon.

27:15.270 --> 27:16.480
Hello, 911?

27:16.790 --> 27:18.240
This is Purong Hotel.

27:18.240 --> 27:19.970
A pregnant woman just fainted.

27:20.270 --> 27:21.550
Okay. Okay.

27:22.810 --> 27:24.030
[Ambulance]

27:23.640 --> 27:25.200
Excuse me!

27:30.400 --> 27:32.160
Careful.

27:32.270 --> 27:33.480
Which one of you is going with her?

27:33.480 --> 27:34.270
I'll go.

27:35.400 --> 27:36.240
Don't.

27:37.270 --> 27:38.160
You stay...

27:39.270 --> 27:41.400
to take care of the guests for me, okay?

27:45.270 --> 27:46.720
None of you need to come.

27:47.750 --> 27:48.640
Xiaoyan,

27:49.720 --> 27:51.460
call my husband

27:51.880 --> 27:54.090
and ask him
to take my mom to the hospital.

27:54.090 --> 27:55.310
Okay.

27:55.440 --> 27:56.880
Okay. Come on. Please make way.

27:56.880 --> 27:57.880
-Come on.
-Excuse me.

27:57.880 --> 27:59.140
Come on. Give me a hand.

28:12.400 --> 28:13.240
Let's go.

28:20.880 --> 28:21.830
Xiaoyan,

28:21.850 --> 28:23.000
go to the Front Office

28:23.000 --> 28:24.720
and get all the receptionists
who are available

28:24.720 --> 28:25.780
from other shifts.

28:26.510 --> 28:28.330
Fill in these empty spots.

28:28.400 --> 28:29.720
Once the pressure
at the reception eases up,

28:29.720 --> 28:31.320
the main hall won't be a mess.

28:31.720 --> 28:32.510
Go quickly.

28:34.310 --> 28:35.000
Hello?

28:43.790 --> 28:45.480
Next group of executive floor guests,

28:45.480 --> 28:46.400
please follow me.

28:46.400 --> 28:47.260
Okay. This way.

28:47.920 --> 28:48.920
This way, please.

28:50.270 --> 28:51.200
Okay, thank you.

28:57.030 --> 28:57.920
Young man,

28:59.270 --> 28:59.920
excuse me,

28:59.920 --> 29:01.570
is there a pharmacy nearby?

29:01.920 --> 29:02.720
Pharmacy?

29:02.910 --> 29:03.880
I really don't know.

29:03.880 --> 29:05.510
You can ask at the information desk.

29:05.510 --> 29:06.400
Information desk?

29:06.400 --> 29:07.030
Right.

29:07.720 --> 29:08.310
Xia.

29:08.720 --> 29:09.320
Come here.

29:09.480 --> 29:10.080
Come here.

29:12.750 --> 29:14.470
What's wrong with that gentleman?

29:14.470 --> 29:15.720
He asked where the pharmacy is.

29:15.720 --> 29:16.850
I don't know either.

29:17.000 --> 29:17.640
I'm going up first.

29:17.640 --> 29:18.510
Go ahead.

29:20.720 --> 29:21.480
Hello.

29:21.480 --> 29:22.920
How can I help you?

29:23.550 --> 29:24.920
Where is the information desk?

29:24.920 --> 29:26.160
Are you looking to buy medicine?

29:26.160 --> 29:26.920
Yes.

29:26.920 --> 29:28.240
How did you know?

29:28.720 --> 29:29.720
I need

29:29.720 --> 29:31.640
to get some diabetes medication.

29:32.030 --> 29:33.230
Please wait a moment.

29:35.480 --> 29:36.400
See if any of these

29:36.400 --> 29:37.400
are what you need.

29:38.980 --> 29:39.680
This one.

29:40.510 --> 29:42.240
Okay, I'll place the order now.

29:42.240 --> 29:43.480
It should be delivered
in about half an hour.

29:43.480 --> 29:44.200
Is that okay?

29:44.200 --> 29:45.510
Okay. Great.

29:45.640 --> 29:47.640
I'll have it delivered to your room.

29:48.070 --> 29:48.880
Room 817.

29:48.880 --> 29:49.720
Okay, got it. Thank you.

29:49.720 --> 29:50.480
Thank you.

29:59.030 --> 30:00.380
Xiaoxi, come help me

30:01.160 --> 30:02.360
move this over there.

30:02.400 --> 30:02.930
Let's go.

30:03.870 --> 30:04.920
It's a bit heavy.

30:04.920 --> 30:05.530
Okay.

30:07.750 --> 30:09.150
There's someone behind.

30:12.480 --> 30:13.240
Madam,

30:13.240 --> 30:14.480
I really don't know the answer to this.

30:14.480 --> 30:15.960
I'm just here to enter your information.

30:15.960 --> 30:16.880
If you have any questions,

30:16.880 --> 30:18.810
please go to the information desk.

30:18.880 --> 30:20.440
There's a long line behind you.

30:20.440 --> 30:21.310
Hello?

30:21.510 --> 30:22.510
Guests with questions,

30:22.510 --> 30:24.570
please come to the information desk.

30:25.680 --> 30:26.510
Come, this way.

30:26.510 --> 30:27.270
Please move over there.

30:27.270 --> 30:27.920
Thank you.

30:28.070 --> 30:28.920
Excuse me,

30:28.920 --> 30:30.780
could you get me a cup of hot water?

30:30.880 --> 30:31.440
Sure.

30:37.790 --> 30:39.090
[Passport]

30:44.550 --> 30:45.960
Thank you.

30:46.880 --> 30:47.550
Xiaoyan.

30:48.480 --> 30:49.510
You scared me.

30:49.510 --> 30:50.270
Sorry about that.

30:50.270 --> 30:51.070
What's wrong?

30:51.160 --> 30:52.960
Can you help this gentleman

30:52.960 --> 30:53.720
check in first?

30:53.720 --> 30:56.270
Mr. Jiang Zhongchen
has a herniated lumbar disc.

30:56.270 --> 30:58.130
He needs to lie down immediately.

30:59.960 --> 31:00.830
I can't do that.

31:01.000 --> 31:02.920
Ms. Xu, we have to go in order.

31:03.030 --> 31:04.860
But it's what the guest needs.

31:05.590 --> 31:06.350
Listen to me.

31:06.350 --> 31:07.280
Just ignore him.

31:08.310 --> 31:09.110
Tell you what.

31:09.270 --> 31:10.680
I'll take him to the executive floor

31:10.680 --> 31:11.750
and find a place for him to rest.

31:11.750 --> 31:13.410
Let me know when it's his turn.

31:15.510 --> 31:16.680
Hello, this way please.

31:16.680 --> 31:18.080
Let me carry this for you.

31:20.310 --> 31:22.440
This woman loves showing off too much.

31:23.160 --> 31:24.310
Ungrateful.

31:25.400 --> 31:26.540
Are you the manager?

31:26.690 --> 31:27.550
How can I help you?

31:27.550 --> 31:28.480
Could you please check

31:28.480 --> 31:30.480
if my room faces the sun?

31:30.960 --> 31:31.750
Luo Qingping,

31:31.750 --> 31:32.790
please take this gentleman

31:32.790 --> 31:34.680
to the executive floor,
find him an empty room,

31:34.680 --> 31:36.110
and send me the room number.

31:36.110 --> 31:36.680
Okay.

31:36.920 --> 31:37.960
-You can follow her.
-This way, please.

31:37.960 --> 31:38.960
Okay, thank you.

31:38.960 --> 31:39.890
You're welcome.

31:39.960 --> 31:40.720
Let me check for you.

31:40.720 --> 31:42.790
Okay. I have rheumatism in my legs.

31:42.790 --> 31:43.790
My doctor says I need

31:43.790 --> 31:45.000
to get sunlight every day.

31:45.000 --> 31:47.460
So I'd like to switch
to a south-facing room.

31:47.920 --> 31:49.310
Do you remember which receptionist

31:49.310 --> 31:50.170
checked you in?

31:50.240 --> 31:51.640
The one in the middle.

31:51.640 --> 31:52.370
Right there.

31:53.640 --> 31:54.960
Okay, give this to me.

31:54.960 --> 31:55.920
Please wait a moment.

31:55.920 --> 31:56.550
Okay.

31:57.110 --> 31:58.040
Enjoy your stay.

31:58.160 --> 31:58.880
Thank you.

31:59.000 --> 31:59.680
Xiaoyan.

31:59.680 --> 32:00.880
Why is it you again?

32:01.310 --> 32:02.550
Could you help this lady

32:02.550 --> 32:03.640
switch to a south-facing room?

32:03.640 --> 32:04.940
Go find someone else.

32:05.000 --> 32:06.800
These computers are connected.

32:07.240 --> 32:08.440
You're so fast.

32:08.440 --> 32:09.720
It'd be easy for you to switch it.

32:09.720 --> 32:10.510
I'm fast,

32:10.510 --> 32:11.960
but it's not to clean up your mess.

32:11.960 --> 32:12.640
If you don't know the job,

32:12.640 --> 32:14.270
don't play the hero here.

32:15.270 --> 32:16.930
Hello, please show me your ID.

32:18.030 --> 32:20.090
Please give me a corner room.

32:20.310 --> 32:21.480
I don't sleep well,

32:21.750 --> 32:23.010
so I want it to be quiet.

32:24.720 --> 32:26.030
I'm sorry, sir.

32:26.030 --> 32:28.720
We don't have a room
that meets your needs right now.

32:28.720 --> 32:30.480
You could try swapping

32:30.480 --> 32:32.750
with another alumnus after you check in.

32:32.750 --> 32:33.550
Wait a moment.

32:34.960 --> 32:37.580
Excuse me, may I see your room card?

32:40.540 --> 32:41.960
I might have a guest here

32:41.960 --> 32:43.510
who can swap rooms with you.

32:44.000 --> 32:44.960
Okay.

32:47.660 --> 32:48.970
Please follow me.

32:53.110 --> 32:54.940
Your rooms have been swapped.

32:55.000 --> 32:56.720
This one,

32:56.720 --> 32:58.750
1119, is facing the sun.

32:58.750 --> 33:00.310
This one, 1126, is a corner room.

33:00.310 --> 33:01.510
You can go upstairs to rest.

33:01.510 --> 33:03.790
I'll go over there
and swap your information.

33:03.790 --> 33:04.880
Okay.

33:07.510 --> 33:08.240
Xiaoyan,

33:08.240 --> 33:09.240
please swap the guest information

33:09.240 --> 33:10.440
for rooms 1119

33:10.440 --> 33:11.720
and 1126.

33:12.720 --> 33:13.240
Got it.

33:13.480 --> 33:15.030
Tell them to come over
for facial recognition.

33:15.030 --> 33:15.720
Okay.

33:18.030 --> 33:19.330
Attention, everyone.

33:19.480 --> 33:21.400
When I call your name,

33:21.400 --> 33:22.750
please come over here

33:22.750 --> 33:25.270
to take a photo
and get your passport and room card.

33:25.270 --> 33:27.510
First, Mr. Zhang Mingyuan.

33:28.270 --> 33:29.330
Wait here a moment.

33:30.100 --> 33:31.310
Ms. Wen Yan.

33:31.310 --> 33:32.980
Mr. Wang Zhifan.

33:33.270 --> 33:34.780
Mr. Ma Zhendong.

33:35.000 --> 33:36.480
Okay, please follow me

33:36.480 --> 33:38.270
to do facial recognition here.

33:38.270 --> 33:40.720
Hello, could you tell me
where the elevator is?

33:40.720 --> 33:42.120
The elevator is this way.

33:42.960 --> 33:44.960
Okay. Please come and register too.

33:46.640 --> 33:49.010
Hello, where's the restroom?

33:49.480 --> 33:51.110
There's one this way,

33:51.110 --> 33:51.720
and also one over there.

33:51.720 --> 33:52.900
Both ones will do.

33:53.310 --> 33:55.330
Why was the information desk
moved here?

33:55.330 --> 33:57.160
Ms. Xu asked me to move it.

33:57.160 --> 33:58.790
She said there are a lot of guests today,

33:58.790 --> 34:00.030
most of them elderly,

34:00.030 --> 34:01.270
and they have trouble walking.

34:01.270 --> 34:02.680
Moving it here makes it easier for them,

34:02.680 --> 34:04.720
and we can also help out the reception.

34:04.720 --> 34:05.100
Okay.

34:06.240 --> 34:06.840
Hello.

34:07.000 --> 34:08.710
Two of us have officially checked in.

34:08.710 --> 34:10.710
I was wondering if...

34:11.280 --> 34:12.880
Xu Miyu? Is Xu Miyu here?

34:12.880 --> 34:13.440
Here.

34:13.510 --> 34:14.110
Okay.

34:14.179 --> 34:15.280
You're delivering medicine, right?

34:15.280 --> 34:16.110
Okay, thanks.

34:16.320 --> 34:17.580
What kind of medicine?

34:18.000 --> 34:18.800
I don't know.

34:18.800 --> 34:19.969
Ms. Xu ordered it.

34:20.030 --> 34:21.670
I'll ask her to come get it now.

34:21.670 --> 34:23.190
I'll take it to her. It's on my way.

34:23.190 --> 34:23.630
Okay.

34:38.320 --> 34:39.000
Mr. Ji.

34:39.510 --> 34:41.040
Is there anything you need?

34:41.710 --> 34:43.480
Just checking in on the elderly

34:43.480 --> 34:44.400
guests.

34:50.040 --> 34:52.320
How's your new room?

34:53.150 --> 34:55.210
It's only for a few days. I can make do.

34:57.070 --> 34:58.110
Once the event is over,

34:58.110 --> 34:58.970
I'll move back.

35:01.190 --> 35:03.320
So you moved rooms to make space
for the Lusia University

35:03.320 --> 35:04.550
Alumni Association?

35:04.880 --> 35:05.710
What else?

35:06.820 --> 35:07.550
Makes sense.

35:13.150 --> 35:14.400
[Rest early after taking the medicine.]

35:13.670 --> 35:15.470
Your delivery from downstairs.

35:16.410 --> 35:17.040
Thank you.

35:31.280 --> 35:32.550
Are you feeling okay?

35:34.480 --> 35:36.280
I-I bought medicine for a guest.

35:40.190 --> 35:41.030
It's fine.

35:51.350 --> 35:56.530
[Lusia University Alumni Association
Anniversary Reunion]

35:52.110 --> 35:53.190
Finally done.

35:53.190 --> 35:54.150
I'm exhausted.

35:54.280 --> 35:55.190
I'm so hungry.

35:56.590 --> 35:57.710
Let's go eat.

35:56.630 --> 36:01.060
[Purong Hotel]

35:58.320 --> 35:59.510
Let's go eat!

36:00.070 --> 36:00.600
Good job.

36:00.670 --> 36:01.360
Good job.

36:10.600 --> 36:11.530
Thank you.

36:17.920 --> 36:19.280
What are you guys eating?

36:19.280 --> 36:21.440
Director Bai, what took you so long?

36:21.440 --> 36:23.700
His daughter is sick. Haven't you heard?

36:25.710 --> 36:27.590
Director Bai, how's your daughter?

36:27.590 --> 36:28.710
Has her fever gone down?

36:28.710 --> 36:30.030
She finished her checkup and went home.

36:30.030 --> 36:32.830
Fortunately, it's not
mycoplasma or adenovirus.

36:33.510 --> 36:35.590
You must have been so worried
about your daughter.

36:35.590 --> 36:37.320
It would be a lie to say I wasn't.

36:39.510 --> 36:40.710
But while I was in the hospital,

36:40.710 --> 36:42.440
I kept thinking about you guys.

36:42.510 --> 36:44.590
Over 100 people checking in at once,

36:44.590 --> 36:46.150
most of them elderly.

36:47.190 --> 36:48.550
You've all worked hard.

36:48.550 --> 36:49.840
You did a great job today.

36:49.840 --> 36:51.370
Everything went smoothly.

36:52.280 --> 36:53.080
I'm starving.

36:54.800 --> 36:56.260
Why is there only one left?

36:59.030 --> 37:00.840
Did I take someone's meal?

37:00.860 --> 37:02.900
What are you talking about?

37:03.230 --> 37:04.280
You're our leader.

37:04.280 --> 37:06.340
Of course there's a box lunch for you.

37:07.030 --> 37:08.230
Sorry, Ms. Xu.

37:08.400 --> 37:09.710
We didn't get enough box lunches.

37:09.710 --> 37:12.370
Go to the cafeteria
and see if there are any left.

37:14.110 --> 37:15.210
I feel so bad.

37:15.400 --> 37:17.330
How about I order you some takeout?

37:17.400 --> 37:18.190
No need.

37:19.070 --> 37:19.930
I'm not hungry.

37:22.030 --> 37:24.110
Ms. Xu, you can have mine.

37:24.110 --> 37:25.440
You've been busy all day.

37:25.440 --> 37:26.840
It's fine. You eat it.

37:30.710 --> 37:31.710
Hurry up and eat.

37:34.920 --> 37:35.880
Eat more.

37:41.510 --> 37:42.320
Mr. Ji.

37:44.320 --> 37:45.510
You haven't had dinner yet, have you?

37:45.510 --> 37:46.070
Here.

37:48.190 --> 37:49.070
I have food.

37:51.080 --> 37:53.190
I accidentally ordered extra.

37:53.190 --> 37:54.720
It'd be a waste not to eat it.

37:56.400 --> 37:57.070
Thank you.

37:59.110 --> 38:00.370
Take care of yourself.

38:02.250 --> 38:03.100
Ms. Xu,

38:03.440 --> 38:05.100
Room 1801 is looking for you.

38:06.800 --> 38:07.670
Copy...

38:08.280 --> 38:09.150
Eat first.

38:10.800 --> 38:12.590
Yin Xiang, go to Room 1801.

38:13.650 --> 38:14.570
Copy that.

39:00.180 --> 39:03.270
[Purong Hotel]

39:14.320 --> 39:15.550
Starting tomorrow,

39:15.550 --> 39:17.190
the lobby will be short a manager.

39:17.190 --> 39:18.440
If you don't decide soon,

39:18.440 --> 39:20.440
Bai Yongjun will come crying to you.

39:22.280 --> 39:23.320
What do you think of her?

39:22.420 --> 39:24.510
[Employee Internal Promotion
Application Form]

39:27.150 --> 39:28.150
What do you think?

39:28.320 --> 39:29.880
I think her abilities are average.

39:29.880 --> 39:32.400
She has some authority among those

39:32.400 --> 39:33.660
young receptionists,

39:34.070 --> 39:35.920
but when it comes to
professional and leadership skills,

39:35.920 --> 39:37.710
she's definitely not qualified.

39:37.710 --> 39:39.280
If Xu Miyu hadn't

39:39.280 --> 39:41.190
been backing her up
with the elderly group today,

39:41.190 --> 39:43.400
she couldn't have handled it on her own.

39:45.880 --> 39:47.460
Do you have any other candidates in mind?

39:47.460 --> 39:52.200
[Purong Hotel]

39:48.550 --> 39:49.710
If we want to be fair,

39:49.850 --> 39:52.330
external recruitment would be the fairest.

39:52.710 --> 39:54.570
But we simply don't have the time.

39:54.840 --> 39:57.420
Maybe we should just go with Lu Xiaoyan.

39:57.550 --> 39:58.840
Consider it a favor to Bai Yongjun.

39:58.840 --> 40:01.370
After all, she's
his strong recommendation.

40:04.150 --> 40:05.680
Do you have someone in mind?

40:09.800 --> 40:10.860
Take a look at this.

40:12.440 --> 40:15.480
[Career Direction Assessment Report]

40:12.760 --> 40:15.700
This person's assessment data
is quite impressive.

40:15.920 --> 40:17.670
A natural for the hotel industry.

40:17.670 --> 40:18.550
Bound to go far.

40:19.550 --> 40:20.320
Who's this?

40:21.510 --> 40:22.280
Xu Miyu.
